{"article_id":"iXLASx3kGzy4buwY","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"MILWAUKEEWisconsin Governor Scott Walker has formally endorsed Ted Cruz one week before the state 's critical primary .","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"`` I am proud to endorse Ted Cruz , ''","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"Walker told radio host Charlie Sykes on Tuesday .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"`` After a lot of thought , a lot of time , a lot of prayer about this , I just really decided","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that after all these years of the Obama-Clinton failures , that it 's time","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"that we elect a strong , new leader","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"and I 've chosen to endorse Ted Cruz to be the next president of the United States . ''","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"he 's endorsing Cruz","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"because Walker said","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"he 's a constitutional conservative ,","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"he 's not afraid to take on special interests and then for one practical reason .","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"`` I just fundamentally believe","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"if you look at the facts","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"and you look at the numbers ,","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"that Ted Cruz is [ in the ] best position by far","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"to both win the nomination of the Republican Party","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"and to then go on and defeat Hillary Clinton in the fall this year , ''","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Walker had laid low up","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"after ending his own presidential campaign after just 71 days .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"Initially thought of as an early front-runner for the nomination ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"he failed to gain traction in a crowded primary field after two lackluster debate performances .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"In his speech","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"announcing","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"he would suspend his campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Walker said","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"he was `` being called to lead","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"by helping to clear the field ''","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"before encouraging others to drop out","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"in order for a `` positive conservative alternative to the current front-runner '' to emerge .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"That front-runner was Donald Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"who remains the favorite","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"to win the Republican nomination","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"after months of primary contests","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"that have winnowed the field","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"but left him on top .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"The importance","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"of winning Wisconsin","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"has grown significantly","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"as Trump tries to reach the necessary 1,237 delegates","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"needed to win the nomination","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"without a contested convention .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"A victory in the Badger State for Cruz would bring him closer in delegates","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"and make the probability of a contested convention that much more likely .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"A look inside the Trump and Cruz campaigns from CBS ' digital journalists","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"Trump preempted Walker 's announcement Monday night with a tweet","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"jabbing the governor","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"and reminding everyone of the other candidates","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"who have also left the race .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"After the way","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"I beat Gov . Scott Walker","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"( and Jeb , Rand , Marco and all others )","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"in the Presidential Primaries ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"no way","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"he would ever endorse me !","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"March 28 , 2016","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Whether Walker 's endorsement will ultimately help Cruz is debatable .","depth":4},{"id":61,"text":"The Wisconsin governor currently has an approval rating of 39 percent statewide ,","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"with 55 percent viewing him negatively .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"Julia Azari , an associate professor of political science at Marquette University , says","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"Walker 's endorsement would normally carry weight ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"but this cycle has been different .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"`` One of the things","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"we have seen this year","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"is that endorsements have not been very strong signals to primary voters ''","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Azari said .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"He added","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"that the endorsement would n't be `` terribly impactful ''","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"because `` it does n't seem like much of a decision '' for Walker ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"given that there are just three candidates remaining in the race .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"However , Azari noted","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Walker 's support could help Cruz in southeastern Wisconsin ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"where there is a large conservative base in the suburbs","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"surrounding Milwaukee .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"This is where Walker has deep roots ,","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"compared to the north or western parts of the state .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"On Monday ,","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"when asked about the possibility of Walker 's endorsement ,","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"Cruz said","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"he `` was a big fan '' of the Wisconsin governor","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"and would welcome his support .","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"Cruz pointed out","depth":4},{"id":86,"text":"Walker 's fight with public-sector unions","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"`` inspired people all over the country ''","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"and triggered a recall election","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"which he ultimately won .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"`` What we need in Washington is more of that same courageous fight for principle","depth":4},{"id":91,"text":"that Scott Walker demonstrated here in Wisconsin , ''","depth":4},{"id":92,"text":"Cruz said .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":185,"left":172,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":138,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":112,"right":137,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":0,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":94,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":97,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":96,"right":6,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":96,"left":3,"right":95,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":95,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":101,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":7,"right":100,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":8,"right":99,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":9,"right":98,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":98,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":108,"left":107,"right":19,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":12,"right":106,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":106,"left":13,"right":105,"relation":"same